The paper proposes a method for training deep neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments conducted in the paper involve both vision and language tasks, indicating a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the impact of noisy data and sample imbalance, which are common challenges in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
